<inglise> (3) Whereas it is essential, in order to ensure that consumers make full use of the Internet, that a safer environment for its use is created by combating illegal use of the technical possibilities of the Internet in particular for offences against children and trafficking in human beings or for the dissemination of racist and xenophobic ideas; </inglise>
<eesti> 3) tagamaks, et tarbijad kasutavad Interneti v&otilde;imalusi t&auml;iel m&auml;&auml;ral, on oluline muuta selle kasutamise keskkond turvalisemaks Interneti tehniliste v&otilde;imaluste ebaseadusliku kasutamise vastu v&otilde;itlemise teel, eelk&otilde;ige seoses lastevastaste kuritegude ja inimkaubanduse ning rassistlike ja ksenofoobste ideede levitamisega; </eesti>
<inglise> (4) Whereas consumers should be afforded a high level of protection; whereas the Community should contribute thereto by specific action which supports and supplements the policy pursued by the Member States regarding information for consumers on the safer use of the Internet; </inglise>
<eesti> 4) tarbijatele tuleks tagada kaitstuse k&otilde;rge tase; &uuml;hendus peaks sellele kaasa aitama erimeetmetega, mis toetavad ja edendavad liikmesriikide p&otilde;him&otilde;tteid kasutajatele m&otilde;eldud Interneti turvalisemat kasutamist k&auml;sitleva teabe kohta; </eesti>
<inglise> (5) Whereas promotion of industry self-regulation and content-monitoring schemes, development of filtering tools and rating systems provided by the industry and increased awareness of industry services as well as fostering international cooperation between all parties concerned will play a crucial role in consolidating that safer environment and contribute to removing obstacles to the development and competitiveness of the industry concerned; </inglise>
<eesti> 5) sektori enesekontrollis&uuml;steemide ja materjali j&auml;relevalve kavade edendamine, sektori pakutavate filtreerimisvahendite ja klassifitseerimiss&uuml;steemide arendamine, suurem teadlikkus sektori pakutavatest teenustest ning rahvusvahelise koost&ouml;&ouml; toetamine k&otilde;igi asjaomaste isikute vahel on k&otilde;nealuse turvalisema keskkonna kindlustamisel keskse t&auml;htsusega ja aitab k&otilde;rvaldada asjaomase sektori arengut ja konkurentsiv&otilde;imelisust piiravaid takistusi; </eesti>
